WEBVTT

00:07.091 --> 00:08.171
[SNARLING]

00:10.052 --> 00:11.462
-A|cide.
BILL: Sookie.

00:11.679 --> 00:13.761
SOOKIE:
Alcide.

00:16.934 --> 00:18.515
[BILL GROANS]

00:19.312 --> 00:21.348
SOOKIE:
Bill.

00:25.443 --> 00:27.479
You're just what the doctor ordered...

00:27.695 --> 00:32.735
...my twee fairy vixen.

00:34.702 --> 00:36.033
[G RU NTS]

00:38.289 --> 00:39.699
[CACKLING]

00:39.874 --> 00:44.994
Yeah, there is that aspect of you
which I loathe.

00:45.963 --> 00:47.248
[WHIMPERING]

00:47.798 --> 00:49.925
Look at me.

00:50.134 --> 00:52.876
I want to be the last thing you ever see.

00:55.097 --> 00:59.010
He dies, we die. Most certainly.

01:00.102 --> 01:03.469
But if we take him back alive,
maybe we don't have to die.

01:03.689 --> 01:07.307
-Unlikely.
-But not impossible.

01:09.070 --> 01:10.355
Maybe you're ready to die.

01:10.571 --> 01:13.404
Maybe you're just bored
after a thousand years.

01:13.616 --> 01:17.029
But you do not make that decision for me.

01:22.124 --> 01:23.534
Freeze.

01:24.710 --> 01:27.247
We will take over from here.

03:00.139 --> 03:01.720
[SCREAMS]

03:01.891 --> 03:03.222
[ROCK MUSIC PLAYING OVER SPEAKERS]

03:06.395 --> 03:08.135
[GRUNTING]

03:11.901 --> 03:14.017
Okay, show's over.

03:15.488 --> 03:18.150
Tara, that's enough.

03:20.242 --> 03:23.234
I guess that whole
friendship thing's on hold.

03:23.454 --> 03:27.322
What do you expect when you
come into my house and fuck with me?

03:27.541 --> 03:29.918
Come with me.

03:30.086 --> 03:31.576
[TARA HISSING]

03:31.754 --> 03:33.164
[CROWD LAUGHING]

03:38.010 --> 03:39.966
[CHATTERING INDISTINCTLY]

03:40.846 --> 03:44.259
This is not your house, it is mine.

03:44.475 --> 03:47.683
You work here. Got it?

03:47.895 --> 03:51.479
Yes, Missy Pam.

03:56.237 --> 04:00.230
You did good out there fighting.
Made me proud.

04:01.909 --> 04:06.152
Proud the way a human is proud
of a well-trained dog.

04:07.248 --> 04:09.034
Nothing more.

04:12.128 --> 04:13.584
[ELLER SCREAMS]

04:17.425 --> 04:19.916
No.

04:21.762 --> 04:23.878
He's dead.
Oh, no, that's smoke and--

04:24.098 --> 04:26.464
Bellefleur.

04:33.482 --> 04:36.189
Eller was right, you fucking prick.
You just got us killed.

04:36.360 --> 04:40.194
-That's enough, private.
-Go fuck yourself, sergeant.

04:48.330 --> 04:51.572
You better hope you are not around
when I am fully restored.

04:51.792 --> 04:55.751
And, oh, I will be. Authority.

04:57.548 --> 05:02.212
What fucking authority do you have?
Given to you by what, Lilith?

05:02.428 --> 05:08.094
You idiots. You're no better than humans
with your absurd magical thinking.

05:08.309 --> 05:11.676
There is no Lilith.

05:13.272 --> 05:15.638
That is blasphemy.

05:15.858 --> 05:17.814
You're fucking worse than human.

05:18.027 --> 05:20.860
You might as well be praying
to leprechauns or unicorns...

05:21.071 --> 05:24.939
...or the motherfucking Kardashians.
That makes just as much sense.

05:27.745 --> 05:30.532
Nate, you fucking dumbass.

05:31.624 --> 05:34.957
JD put up a hell of a fight
till he heard those two wolves dying.

05:35.169 --> 05:39.287
-He ran like a fucking squirrel.
-Wolf and human are here.

05:39.507 --> 05:42.123
-Why?
-Doug led us here.

05:42.968 --> 05:45.801
We found them parked in a van
outside of Shreveport.

05:46.013 --> 05:48.299
Humping each other like livestock.

05:48.516 --> 05:51.428
And we took the van to get here
with them in it.

05:51.644 --> 05:56.638
You could cover that much distance
by yourselves much faster than by driving.

05:56.857 --> 05:59.098
We had another human with us
that we needed...

05:59.318 --> 06:02.902
...because he'd remembered
coming here before. Doug.

06:03.948 --> 06:06.439
They know too much.

06:06.659 --> 06:09.992
Nothing that a little glamouring
won't take care of.

06:15.501 --> 06:17.457
Do it.

06:17.670 --> 06:21.208
-Barker, make sure it happens.
BARKER: Yes, sir, chancellor.

06:23.717 --> 06:26.333
Sookie, look me in the eyes.

06:26.554 --> 06:28.385
Bill, are you--?

06:35.354 --> 06:37.265
Let's just get this over with.

06:39.149 --> 06:41.140
We owe you, wolf.

06:54.832 --> 06:58.495
You will remember nothing of this night.

06:58.711 --> 07:02.078
Nothing of me or Eric.

07:02.798 --> 07:05.585
It'll be as though we never met.

07:12.474 --> 07:16.467
-Who is Doug?
-Oh, God.

07:17.313 --> 07:18.644
That's me.

07:18.856 --> 07:20.972
I understand you've been
brought here before.

07:21.191 --> 07:24.149
Yes, by a vampire, a woman.

07:24.361 --> 07:27.444
But I don't want to remember.
I want to forget.

07:27.656 --> 07:30.523
I can identify her.
I'll never forget that face.

07:30.743 --> 07:33.485
Yeah. Or the look in her eyes
when she said...

07:33.704 --> 07:36.571
...we were all gonna die
for the glory of God.

07:36.790 --> 07:39.327
See, they remember her.
So why don't you let me go?

07:39.543 --> 07:42.706
As soon as your interrogation
has been completed.

07:42.921 --> 07:47.665
And then will you please do that thing
so that I won't remember any of this?

07:47.885 --> 07:50.092
You have my word.

07:51.305 --> 07:55.639
You will remember nothing of us
showing up tonight...

07:55.851 --> 07:58.137
...or anything that happened aftenNard.

07:58.354 --> 08:01.016
And you will always protect Sookie...

08:02.441 --> 08:04.397
...with your life.

08:04.610 --> 08:06.475
Yes.

08:07.196 --> 08:09.278
But you'll keep your hands off her.

08:10.032 --> 08:15.026
Romantically speaking.
She kind of disgusts you.

08:17.539 --> 08:18.995
Okay.

08:19.833 --> 08:24.167
And you will live your life
as you were meant to live it.

08:26.215 --> 08:27.921
In the sun.

08:28.967 --> 08:31.219
With others like you.

08:33.263 --> 08:35.094
Human.

08:42.064 --> 08:43.429
[GROANING]

08:43.607 --> 08:44.767
[CHATTERING INDISTINCTLY]

08:44.942 --> 08:47.024
-Let me just-- Luna.
-Emma.

08:47.236 --> 08:49.727
Let go. Get your fucking hands off me.

08:49.947 --> 08:54.566
-You've lost a lot of blood. Remain still.
-Luna.

08:55.077 --> 08:57.409
[WOLF PUP YELPING]

09:05.838 --> 09:07.624
MARTHA:
What?

09:08.549 --> 09:10.414
Hey.

09:10.634 --> 09:13.592
Oh, hey there.

09:13.804 --> 09:17.342
Oh, baby girl.

09:17.516 --> 09:19.131
[WOLF PUP WHIMPERING]

09:19.309 --> 09:22.016
It's okay. It's okay.

09:22.229 --> 09:24.936
Grandma's got you now.

09:26.525 --> 09:28.811
Come on in, Emma.

09:32.531 --> 09:34.396
[DANCE MUSIC PLAYING OVER SPEAKERS]

09:49.089 --> 09:50.124
What are you doing?

09:50.299 --> 09:53.041
Exercising my constitutional right
to be a dirty fangbanger.

09:53.260 --> 09:58.425
-Well, you look ridiculous.
-Well, that's one opinion.

09:58.640 --> 10:02.349
You can't get me down, Jess.
Not tonight.

10:03.812 --> 10:06.349
-l'm just so happy.
-Really?

10:06.523 --> 10:07.854
Mm-hm.

10:08.066 --> 10:10.227
I learned something tonight.

10:10.444 --> 10:12.526
You want to know what?

10:12.738 --> 10:16.401
I don't think it matters if I do or don't.
You're gonna tell me anyways.

10:16.617 --> 10:19.324
You still care about me.

10:21.413 --> 10:23.119
Oh, Hoyt.

10:23.332 --> 10:26.244
No, you would have let Tara drain me,
but you didn't.

10:26.460 --> 10:28.951
Oh, you don't want to be in love with me,
but you are.

10:29.171 --> 10:31.162
JESSICA: This is so pathetic.
HOYT: It's okay.

10:31.381 --> 10:34.123
And I know you want to be
more of a vampire. That's okay.

10:34.343 --> 10:36.959
You want to feed on me 24/7,
l'll love that.

10:37.179 --> 10:40.216
-You can be as rough as you want to be.
-Hoyt.

10:40.432 --> 10:42.218
We're over.

10:42.434 --> 10:45.676
Now you hear me.
It is never gonna happen.

10:45.854 --> 10:48.231
[CHUCKLING]

10:48.398 --> 10:52.266
Like, yeah, that's what you say.
But what's in your heart is something--

10:52.486 --> 10:54.192
Hey, you want to glamour me?

10:54.404 --> 10:57.487
You want to hypnotize me into doing
anything that you've wanted...

10:57.699 --> 11:01.487
...with a human being, no matter
how depraved, I don't give a fuck.

11:01.703 --> 11:04.831
But will you please just do it with me?

11:10.212 --> 11:13.625
Hoyt, this is not you.

11:16.510 --> 11:19.252
This is me, goddamn it.

11:19.471 --> 11:21.803
MAN:
Dude, chill.

11:27.396 --> 11:29.227
[CRYING]

11:30.649 --> 11:32.731
Why you crying?

11:34.903 --> 11:37.144
Where the fuck are we?

11:38.699 --> 11:40.815
How did we get here?

11:44.538 --> 11:48.998
No one thought you two would actually
be able to deliver Russell Edgington.

11:49.209 --> 11:51.746
Guardian will be extremely pleased.

11:51.962 --> 11:54.578
Pleased enough to not execute us?

11:55.132 --> 11:58.795
-Only Lilith knows that.
-As only she knows all.

12:05.350 --> 12:08.137
Enough with this religious bullshit already.

12:09.730 --> 12:13.188
Lilith can fucking blow me.

12:13.400 --> 12:17.484
-And why are you suddenly so into it?
-l'm just covering my ass.

12:34.630 --> 12:36.370
Yes, sir.

12:37.591 --> 12:39.957
DOUG: I saw Russell Edgington.
-Ladies and gentlemen...

12:40.177 --> 12:43.135
...please accept my apologies
for the inexcusable acts...

12:43.347 --> 12:45.633
...of the vampires that have terrorized you.

12:45.849 --> 12:48.386
Will we receive
any kind of financial restitution?

12:48.602 --> 12:51.560
-| just want to get out of here.
-Of course.

12:51.772 --> 12:54.184
Please fasten your seatbelts.

12:55.192 --> 12:57.023
[SCREAMING]

13:08.705 --> 13:09.740
[GASPS]

13:12.292 --> 13:16.786
I had a dream
you and Mom were still alive and--

13:16.964 --> 13:18.420
Heh.

13:20.842 --> 13:24.926
Daddy, you called me champ.
Champ.

13:25.138 --> 13:27.129
Like you used to.

13:27.349 --> 13:30.557
Only I had forgotten you ever did that.

13:31.353 --> 13:33.344
How could I forget that?

13:33.563 --> 13:39.854
It always made me feel
like I was something you were proud of.

13:40.946 --> 13:43.904
Yeah. Made me feel good.

13:44.116 --> 13:47.529
Not in a "making me forget all the bad
stuff I'm feeling"...

13:47.744 --> 13:50.451
...kind of way I'm used to now.

13:50.664 --> 13:52.404
But in a:

13:53.375 --> 13:57.914
"I'm just feeling good about myself
and that's all" kind of way.

14:00.382 --> 14:02.168
Forgotten what that even feels like.

14:07.931 --> 14:14.894
I swear to God and to you both
I will find that vampire that killed you...

14:15.605 --> 14:18.847
...and I will make them pay
for what they did to our family.

14:19.943 --> 14:24.937
The only thing you have to fear is--

15:00.067 --> 15:01.978
Morning.

15:02.652 --> 15:04.779
Coffee and Advil's over there.

15:04.988 --> 15:08.401
You want something to eat,
you're gonna need to make it yourself.

15:17.709 --> 15:19.119
-You okay?
-No.

15:19.336 --> 15:22.328
Honestly, I can't even remember
the last time l was okay.

15:22.547 --> 15:24.959
Totally okay.

15:25.175 --> 15:26.381
Anything you need?

15:26.593 --> 15:29.005
A fucking normal life.

15:29.179 --> 15:30.794
[GROANS]

15:31.598 --> 15:33.964
[MOANING]

15:34.142 --> 15:36.303
Wow, we, um--

15:37.646 --> 15:39.637
Drank a lot last night, huh?

15:39.856 --> 15:41.721
Not enough.

15:45.112 --> 15:46.727
Whoa.

15:47.239 --> 15:49.104
Sook

15:51.701 --> 15:52.827
Did...?

15:53.829 --> 15:55.285
Did--?

15:55.747 --> 15:57.738
-Did we--?
-No.

15:57.958 --> 16:00.916
Some other stuff happened.

16:08.593 --> 16:10.970
What kind of other stuff?

16:18.311 --> 16:22.645
Did you just recoil from me?

16:22.858 --> 16:24.223
Why?

16:26.194 --> 16:29.561
Fucking Eric. Close your eyes.

16:38.874 --> 16:42.492
-Oh, fucking JD.
-Thank you.

16:43.795 --> 16:46.002
Fucking wolves on V again.

16:46.214 --> 16:48.125
Russell fucking Edgington? Fuck.

16:48.341 --> 16:52.675
What the fuck is wrong with Eric and Bill?
They purposefully kept him alive.

16:52.888 --> 16:55.550
Explain to me how that makes sense
in any universe.

16:55.765 --> 16:59.599
There's no way I could ever explain
either one of them.

17:00.562 --> 17:03.599
There's no way I could sit around
and watch it happen again.

17:03.815 --> 17:06.147
lt's fucking Jackson all over.

17:07.444 --> 17:08.854
Bye.

17:09.070 --> 17:13.359
I'm just gonna stay here
and quietly slip into a coma.

17:14.576 --> 17:16.191
SAM:
Luna?

17:16.411 --> 17:17.912
-Sir.
-How you feeling?

17:18.121 --> 17:20.203
-Emma.
-I saw her. She got away. I saw her.

17:20.415 --> 17:22.406
-Go back to your room.
-|'|| need a chair.

17:22.626 --> 17:24.867
-Did she go or--?
-You need to reconnect your lV.

17:25.086 --> 17:29.204
Whatever is in my IV is important,
you can bring it from my room to me here.

17:29.424 --> 17:34.134
You're not gonna be able to keep me
away from her, so don't even try.

17:37.432 --> 17:38.933
Sam.

17:39.142 --> 17:42.225
I'll find Emma. I promise you.

17:42.437 --> 17:44.223
Okay.

17:45.649 --> 17:49.938
Why would--?
Who would want to kill shifters?

17:50.153 --> 17:53.816
Who even knows about shifters?
Only other supes. Wolves.

17:54.032 --> 17:57.445
No. Luna, they were human.

17:58.036 --> 18:00.402
I think there were about four of them.

18:00.622 --> 18:03.364
Now, I didn't see much.
They were wearing masks.

18:03.583 --> 18:07.917
But I smelled whiskey, chewing tobacco,
bad breath, bad diets.

18:08.129 --> 18:10.586
EMMA: Mommy.
-Baby. Oh, my God.

18:10.799 --> 18:14.166
EMMA: Mommy, are you okay? I was so scared.
-Only family members allowed.

18:14.386 --> 18:17.719
You need to get away from me
before I hurt you.

18:20.892 --> 18:25.056
She ran to my house several miles
through some bad parts of town.

18:25.272 --> 18:28.730
-She came to me as wolf.
EMMA: I'm sorry, Mommy.

18:28.942 --> 18:31.604
My Barbie who is a wolf told me to.

18:32.320 --> 18:36.313
Just because she is a wolf
does not mean that you can have her.

18:36.533 --> 18:39.366
| only want to be a part of her life.

18:41.246 --> 18:43.862
EMMA: Mommy.
-Sweet pea.

18:44.082 --> 18:48.325
Mammaw promised that you would
get better if I'm not too loud.

18:56.261 --> 18:57.671
What do you think I should do?

18:57.887 --> 19:02.347
Oh, l.... l thinkthis is
between you and Martha and Emma.

19:04.144 --> 19:07.636
Well, I guess I don't have
much of a choice, do |?

19:08.565 --> 19:11.398
Honey, l'm her grandmama.

19:11.609 --> 19:14.646
There's a piece of my boy in her.

19:16.031 --> 19:20.024
But you're the one who gave birth to her.
That ain't ever gonna change.

19:20.243 --> 19:23.360
I don't want to compete with you,
even if I could, |--

19:23.580 --> 19:28.825
ljust don't want to lose her and Marcus.

19:36.926 --> 19:40.510
There is someone after shifters.

19:40.722 --> 19:44.306
Can you keep her safe
until we figure out who that is?

19:44.517 --> 19:45.893
Of course.

19:48.730 --> 19:50.561
Okay.

19:51.775 --> 19:54.858
TERRY: lt fucking saw us, knows who we are.
It's gonna come after us now.

19:55.070 --> 19:57.561
PATRICK: Jesus, Bellefleur,
would you just shut the fuck up?

19:57.781 --> 19:59.442
-You're spiraling.
-Stop the truck.

20:00.116 --> 20:02.653
-Why?
-Stop, quick. I gotta get out.

20:02.869 --> 20:05.952
-What, are you sick?
-Stop the goddamn truck.

20:07.165 --> 20:08.154
[G RU NTS]

20:08.333 --> 20:09.789
PATRICK:
Bellefleur.

20:11.419 --> 20:13.410
Hey.

20:19.469 --> 20:23.178
Bellefleur. Bellefleur.

20:32.273 --> 20:34.264
Goddamn it,
alone you are a dead man.

20:34.484 --> 20:35.724
A dead man.

20:35.944 --> 20:37.855
-I never should've done it.
-We need to--

20:38.071 --> 20:41.188
We need to have each other's backs
at all times. Do you understand?

20:41.408 --> 20:44.241
I never should have done it.
I never should have done it.

20:44.411 --> 20:45.491
[SPEAKING IN ARABIC]

20:45.662 --> 20:47.118
Dead-check her.

20:48.206 --> 20:49.662
PATRICK:
Do it.

20:51.876 --> 20:55.494
God-fucking-damn, sergeant.
She put a curse on us.

20:55.713 --> 20:57.749
We are cursed
and there's no escape from it.

20:57.966 --> 20:59.331
-Private.
-Fuck you.

20:59.551 --> 21:02.793
I'm not your goddamn private no more.

21:03.012 --> 21:07.722
You ordered me
to do something evil and wrong.

21:07.934 --> 21:10.971
And it's gonna end up
getting me killed.

21:11.855 --> 21:14.767
And you too,
you stupid son of a bitch.

21:15.233 --> 21:17.690
You're a fucking dead man.

21:24.492 --> 21:28.576
Oh, man.
I knew it was too good to be true.

21:30.206 --> 21:33.573
Arlene, the kids.

21:33.793 --> 21:35.658
Mikey.

21:37.255 --> 21:40.668
| just ain't the kind of guy
that gets to have something like that.

21:42.385 --> 21:44.967
Not for long, at least.

21:49.976 --> 21:52.342
I'll see you back at the truck.

22:00.111 --> 22:03.103
Excuse me. Ruby Jean Reynolds.
I'm her son.

22:03.323 --> 22:06.486
Y'all called and said
there was an emergency. Is she okay?

22:06.701 --> 22:08.441
Is she okay?

22:17.795 --> 22:20.252
Oh, Mama.

22:20.423 --> 22:22.209
What?

22:24.135 --> 22:26.968
They told me you had a seizure.

22:28.306 --> 22:31.423
-I did.
-Well, is you okay?

22:31.643 --> 22:35.386
| tell you who not okay. Jesus.

22:36.731 --> 22:40.474
