He come here last night.

22:50.119 --> 22:51.154
l seen't him too.

22:51.371 --> 22:55.205
Somebody stitched up his lips.
But he wants to talk to you.

22:55.416 --> 22:57.543
Well, where he at? |--

22:57.752 --> 23:02.041
He with a evil man
who made him drink goat blood.

23:02.257 --> 23:05.795
That's what started all this mess
to begin with.

23:06.010 --> 23:08.717
-Don Bartolo.
-That's a bad man.

23:08.930 --> 23:12.093
That's a bad man.

23:12.308 --> 23:17.302
-Mama, how do you know all this?
-I ain't got no fucking clue, baby.

23:17.522 --> 23:22.141
The electricity just runs through me.
It always have.

23:22.360 --> 23:25.693
I be seeing shit
I ain't got no right to be seeing.

23:25.905 --> 23:29.238
Shit that I ain't even know
what it even is.

23:29.450 --> 23:33.443
You gots to go.
Jesus is in trouble. Save Jesus.

23:33.663 --> 23:38.657
-I will.
-Jesus. Jesus loves you.

23:42.797 --> 23:46.085
Even if you're a abomination.

23:48.177 --> 23:49.633
Come here.

23:49.846 --> 23:51.882
You been smoking that bone lately?

23:52.098 --> 23:53.929
La La.

23:54.142 --> 23:57.134
-Te|| Ruby J.
